		README for KGDB for blackfin uclinux

		Sonic Zhang <sonic.zhang@analog.com>

			Apr. 13th 2005

This KGDB patch should be applied to the uclinux kernel 2.6.x for blackfin
architecure.  The corresponding GDB client is in the blackfin toolchain 
project, it should be compiled before you can do the debugging.

After you apply this patch, you can find a simple guide on how to configure
kgdb to debug kernel in file linux-2.6.x/Documentation/blackfin/kgdb_bfin.txt .
